property.name: note
property.value:
Stage 1, 2, and 3 switches advance the plot linearly. When we reach Stage 3, we branch to either Stage 4 (Exposing your arch-rival), or Blackmail, which blackmails them.
Following the Expose path: The Stage 5 switch takes us to the Triumphant/victorous section. We will then get caught in another "safety" repeat, which we can get out of by triggering the END switch to cause us to skip to the ending coda as soon as we finish the nearest phrase.
Following the Blackmail Path: From Stage 3, we throw the Blackmail switch, which takes us to the Blackmail section, and a "safety" repeat, which we get out of by triggereing the "END" switch, to move us to the ending of the Blackmail section.
